Package com.eclipsesource.tabris.ui.action

Interface SearchActionListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ActionListener, java.io.Serializable
    public interface SearchActionListener
extends ActionListener

    A SearchActionListener is a specialized ActionListener that can be used to get notified when the user has modified the search query or executed a search. SearchActionListener can be added as usual ActionListener to a UIConfiguration.

    Since:
    1.4
    See Also:
    UIConfiguration, SearchAction
